<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c01"/><p id="pI01p0113c0101">蓋前劫莫初。心路非始。攸哉<note n="0113004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06431;＝邈【史】</note><app n="0113004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06431;</rdg></app>乎。靡測<note n="0113005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30720;＝其【史】</note><app n="0113005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">其</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30720;</rdg></app>源者也。自天地<note n="0113006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30721;＝替【史】</note><app n="0113006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">替</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30721;</rdg></app>成。陰陽&CB30397;運。□靈
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c02"/>起滅。業報相依。莫不染習<note n="0113007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30726;＝色【史】</note><app n="0113007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30726;</rdg></app>塵。驚馳愛慾。循環五趣。亦沉溺四流。雖<note n="0113008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30712;＝復【史】</note><app n="0113008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30712;</rdg></app>緣起一
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c03"/>生。受神□識。形心電速。念念□留。假使靈芝九轉。行極四誠。奔□月以高昇。<note n="0113009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30722;＝望【史】</note><app n="0113009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30722;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c04"/>玄宮而蹔息。猶亦<note n="0113010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30723;＝退【史】</note><app n="0113010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">退</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30723;</rdg></app>沒三塗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">旋</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">還</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">六</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">不</unclear>說<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">生</unclear>死之因緣。詎云<note n="0113011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30724;＝解【史】</note><app n="0113011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">解</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30724;</rdg></app>脫之果報。能
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c05"/>仁悟&CB00528;前機。超□後際。降靈□室。□□□□□□駕四門。卻遺三殿。一心高蹈。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c06"/>成&CB07099;上尊。至<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>化動<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">十</unclear>方。迴□三□。吞□大<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">海</unclear>。□納須<note n="0113012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30394;＝彌【史】</note><app n="0113012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app>。雖神照冥通。至德潛
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c07"/>衍。莫不稱相<note n="0113013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30627;＝取【史】</note><app n="0113013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">取</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30627;</rdg></app><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">益</unclear>。□物□□。□□□之□。□真實之相。因化城以蹔止。演眾妙
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c08"/>於鷲山。及<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慧</unclear>日□□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear>□□□。□□五□。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">屬</unclear>三千。藉有作之功。會無為之力。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c09"/>航法<note n="0113014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11971;＝船【史】</note><app n="0113014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">船</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11971;</rdg></app>於淨□。□常<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樂</unclear>□□□。□□天<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">人</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慕</unclear>感。<note n="0113015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30725;＝像【史】</note><app n="0113015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30725;</rdg></app>法興靈。惟敬真顏。寄存寶<app source="0113007" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30726;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c10"/><note n="0113016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30727;＝然【史】</note><app n="0113016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">然</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30727;</rdg></app>州武猛從<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">事</unclear>汲郡□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">六</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">鄉</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>秀老。遂割損<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">家</unclear>資。率諸<app source="0113001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30728;</rdg></app>義五百餘
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c11"/>人。&CB00278;著信情<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">源</unclear>。崇宗□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">千</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">劫</unclear>。故正順一時。起津梁於生滅之<note n="0113017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00639;＝淵【史】</note><app n="0113017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00639;</rdg></app>。運<note n="0113018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB09274;＝舟【史】</note><app n="0113018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB09274;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c12"/><note n="0113019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00188;＝楫【史】</note><app n="0113019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">楫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00188;</rdg></app>於貪慾之海。通四衢□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">駕</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">擁</unclear>三彰。竭八倒之流。兼義冠<note n="0113020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30729;＝鄉【史】</note><app n="0113020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鄉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30729;</rdg></app>閭。譽聞<note n="0113021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30307;＝邦【史】</note><app n="0113021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30307;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c13"/><app source="0113001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30728;</rdg></app>。莫不尚祇<note n="0113022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00035;＝園【史】</note><app n="0113022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00035;</rdg></app>而結<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慕</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">同</unclear>□□□歸依。遂瞻影天竺。尚想□城。眷茲一山。僉共
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c14"/>嘉力。<app source="0113005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">其</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30720;</rdg></app>峻壁單懸。遙<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">峰</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">疊</unclear>□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">流</unclear>□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">野</unclear>。帶□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">山</unclear>□。至如寶塔五層。則浮空曜晷。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c15"/><note n="0113023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【史】</note><app n="0113023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>棠百刃。則撫日承天。□木□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">地</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">足</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">並</unclear>雀離之高妙矣。又真儀應<app source="0113015" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30725;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c16"/>則暉&CB00153;龕室。神光照<note n="0113024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07876;＝爛【史】</note><app n="0113024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">爛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07876;</rdg></app>。則□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">太</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">清</unclear>。□空隱現。無<app source="0113008" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30712;</rdg></app>等級。威神相好。不可思議。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c17"/><app source="0113008" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30712;</rdg></app>即石以拓玄<note n="0113025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30731;＝基【史】</note><app n="0113025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">基</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30731;</rdg></app>。因木而架□□。引長廊而交&CB00153;。接戶<note n="0113026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04523;＝牖【史】</note><app n="0113026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">牖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04523;</rdg></app>以相經。堂廡霞舒。階
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c18"/>墀綺合。雲生枅向。風出<note n="0113027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30732;＝簷【史】</note><app n="0113027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">簷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30732;</rdg></app>軒。花□秀美。光開七淨。泉流藻注。鴻澧八<app source="0113011" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">解</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30724;</rdg></app>。雖謝菩
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c19"/>提吉祥之勝地。方同竹<app source="0113022" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00035;</rdg></app>伽藍之妙哉。於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear>名僧德眾。煙<note n="0113028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30733;＝集【史】</note><app n="0113028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">集</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30733;</rdg></app>如林。栖息<note n="0113029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB21061;＝戒【史】</note><app n="0113029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB21061;</rdg></app>藏之
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c20"/>門。優遊正定之路。結漏永消。脫諸塵網。般若之力既充。所作之功亦辨。六時精
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c21"/>苦。不閑日夜。四事奉給。無<note n="0113030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朁＝替【史】</note><app n="0113030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">替</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朁</rdg></app>所須。而樹福良田。脩功淨土。亡情投<note n="0113031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30734;＝軫【史】</note><app n="0113031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30734;</rdg></app>。<app source="0113013" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">取</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30627;</rdg></app>會將來。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c22"/>既事光<note n="0113032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30735;＝世【史】</note><app n="0113032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30735;</rdg></app>上。業<app source="0113003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB21284;</rdg></app>寰中。鴻名盛德。方傳不朽。祇掌寄言。雖不盡意。題表<app source="0113023" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>石。<app source="0113005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">其</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30720;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c23"/>能已哉。乃作銘曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c24"/>心塗<note n="0113033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30736;＝眇【史】</note><app n="0113033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">眇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30736;</rdg></app>極。性緒攸玄。三才始運。一<note n="0113034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30737;＝氣【史】</note><app n="0113034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">氣</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30737;</rdg></app>□延。虛成報果。妄結因緣。有形分段。&CB07099;<app source="0113007" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30726;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c25"/>已遷。於唯大覺。隨感現身。<note n="0113035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30742;＝權【史】</note><app n="0113035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30742;</rdg></app>影昏俗。混相纓塵。汎茲永夜。濟彼長津。緣乖化<note n="0113036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18842;＝隱【史】</note><app n="0113036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">隱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18842;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c26"/>卷跡歸真。<app source="0113032" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30735;</rdg></app>崇遺教。<note n="0113037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30738;＝瞻【史】</note><app n="0113037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瞻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30738;</rdg></app><note n="0113038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30744;＝圖【史】</note><app n="0113038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30744;</rdg></app>影則。寶<note n="0113039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB09400;＝剎【史】</note><app n="0113039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB09400;</rdg></app>層巖。<app source="0113023" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>槃累<note n="0113040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30745;＝飾【史】</note><app n="0113040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">飾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30745;</rdg></app><app source="0113027" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">簷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30732;</rdg></app>宇高臨。長楹峻極。庭流
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c27"/>桂水。<app source="0113022" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00035;</rdg></app>開淨<app source="0113007" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30726;</rdg></app>。既曰福地。實唯淨土。息<app source="0113036" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">隱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18842;</rdg></app><note n="0113041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08668;＝桑【史】</note><app n="0113041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">桑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08668;</rdg></app>門。淹留<note n="0113042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30746;＝緇【史】</note><app n="0113042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30746;</rdg></app>旅。功不虛<note n="0113043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30739;＝棄【史】</note><app n="0113043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">棄</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30739;</rdg></app>。果不妄袪。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c28"/>德標千劫。聲傳万古。
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c29"/>維大<note n="0113044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30740;＝魏【史】</note><app n="0113044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">魏</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30740;</rdg></app>永熙二年歲在甲寅興建。至武定元年歲次癸亥八月功就。仰為
<lb ed="C I" n="0113c30"/>皇家。願國祚永<note n="0113045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30741;＝延【史】</note><app n="0113045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">延</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30741;</rdg></app>化隆遐劫。<note n="0113046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00605;＝疆【史】</note><app n="0113046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">疆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00605;</rdg></app>靜境安。民寧道澤。法界有形。等成正覺。</p>
